plans considered likely to emerge from each budget panel would 
shrink the deficit by 37 billion relying on roughly equal amounts 
of defense cuts and new taxes and lesser savings from cuts in 
medicare payments to farmers and other domestic programs 
ill be able to get a budget resolution out of committee 
