an upbeat mood settled over this 
launch center sunday when crews finished installing the 15 
billion hubble space telescope in the space shuttle discovery and 
said they were on track for a tuesday morning liftoff 
this is a very important day for us said william taylor 
the telescopes chief engineer some of us who have been on the 
