criticized the report based on the allegations of an unidentified 
former secret police agent 
two prominent east german leaders including former social 
democrat leader ibrahim boehme have resigned in recent months amid 
similar allegations which they denied de maiziere also has denied 
allegations he had ties to the secret police known as the stasi 
