proposed changes resulted from the slotmachine troubles at the 
1250room casino hotel atlantic citys biggest that opened 
last monday 
the tajs 3000 slot machines were shut down friday night after 
the volume of action overburdened the casino the machines had 
opened six hours late that day because of staff shortages and 
problems accounting for the amount of money in the machines 
they remained closed during the weekend and will be out of 
service indifinitely to allow for procedural changes officials 
said 
taj mahal executive vice president w bucky howard is to become 
president and chief operations officer at the casino said 
spokeswoman karon tuso 
as a casino operator bucky is one of the best trump said 
in the statement read by ms tuso he will provide the leadership 
that will ensure the trump taj mahal its place as the worlds 
greatest casino and convention resort 
howard would replace walter j haybert who has been president 
and chief executive officer since last october haybert would 
become chief financial officer 
edward tracy would be named president and chief executive 
officer of trump hotel corp while continuing as president and 
